latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The calmness I need in my life right now 

via @carissavianca

My sister @jennysun and I have always been lovers of beautiful paper/design goods from a very young age, so it’s always been a dream of ours to start creating some that were our own.

I’m so excited to share with you our new brand reveal @stonepress.studio with our first collection launching very soon! This has been in the works for the past year or so now and I’m really proud that we’re able to bring this dream to life 🤍 

If you’d like to follow along our journey and be a part of our first collection reveal, please go ahead and give us a follow to support 🥰 Can’t wait to hear what you all think! 

#stonepressstudio

latestPosts.caption:
diaries of a designer learning to fall back in love with design again 🤍

after a year of big changes in 2024 — moving out, a new job, wedding planning, and pouring my creativity into every hour of every day with work and if it wasn’t work it was wedding diy — i entered this year completely burnt out.

over the past few months, i’ve been trying to find my way back and slowly reigniting that spark again — reconnecting with design and remembering why i fell in love with it in the first place 😌 it’s been a process of stepping back, creating space, and learning to find balance again.

still a work in progress learning to create from rest — not rush. but finally, it feels like the joy is (slowly) returning again. 

#vlog #dailyvlog #dayinmylifevlog #dayinthelifevlog #uxuidesigner
